Package: vmbackup
Version: __VERSION__
Architecture: all
Maintainer: James Doutsis <james@doutsis.com>
Depends: bash (>= 5.0), libvirt-daemon-system, qemu-utils, sqlite3, jq, coreutils, util-linux, virtnbdbackup (>= 2.28)
Recommends: msmtp, rclone
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/doutsis/vmbackup
Description: Production-grade backup manager for libvirt/KVM virtual machines
 Automated full + incremental backups using virtnbdbackup with monthly directory
 structure, weekly checkpoint consolidation, per-VM rotation policies, QEMU guest
 agent integration, SharePoint/cloud replication, email reporting, and configurable
 retention management. Supports multiple config instances for dev/test/prod.
